" Bubble single lines
" requires tpope's vim-unimpaired installed
" https://github.com/tpope/vim-unimpaired
nmap <C-k> [e
nmap <C-j> ]e

" Bubble multiple lines
vmap <C-k> [egv
vmap <C-j> ]egv

